<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Schawmb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, Apeln, Karl und
                                <expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Schawmb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>gebrüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Apel, Karl und
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, uns hat fürbracht die erwirdig
                        geistlich fraw, die abtessin des <expan>klost<ex>er</ex>s</expan> czü
                        Grindlach, des wir versprecher sein, wie ir ir
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> eins
                                <expan>abtrünnige<ex>n</ex></expan> münches
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der aws <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>klost<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Bancz <expan>geloffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sey, und maint, daz sie den czü Grindlach hielt etc. Nu hat uns die abtessin
                        gesagt, daz sie <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> sache nicht
                                <expan>czeschicke<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, <add>als sie ew das
                                    <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                    <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wölle</add>.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wol,
                        daz ir der abtessin und <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>klost<ex>er</ex></expan> keins argen <expan>gewart<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        und unser <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>
<expan>schone<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, wan uns das
                            <expan>klost<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> stet. Das wölle etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Valent<ex>in</ex>i</expan>. </ab>
</div>
